 golf  Attempts are made for the experienced players to compete in tournaments against other club teams during the fall and spring semesters  The team is coached by David Johnstone and assisted by Tim Hodges  League  National Collegiate Club Golf Association Head Coach  Dave Johnstone Assistant Coach  Tim Hodges Cadet In Charge   Cadet Yates Assistant Cadet In Charge    UPCOMING EVENTS  RESULTS  The weekend of February 23 24the Golf club travels to Raleigh  North Carolina  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 